dataanalyzer.entity
Class AlgorithmProcess

java.lang.Object
  dataanalyzer.entity.AlgorithmProcess
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable
public abstract class AlgorithmProcess
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable, java.io.Serializable

This abstract class provides the base code for processing an algorithm. The bulk of the code should be called from inside the cycle() method. The cycle() method will constantly be called untill the process it requested to stop or the cycle() method returns false, thus providing a controlled loop structure.
